    different in conditions.<br>\r\nDistance from Sun: <b>~108 million km</b><br>\r\nOrbital
    speed: <b>35 km/s</b><br>\r\nA year on Venus is <b>225 Earth days</b>.<br>\r\nIt
    has a thick toxic atmosphere and is the hottest planet (~465\xB0C).<br><br>"
  planetName: Venus
