  planetInfo: '<b><u>Mars</u></b><br>

    Mars is known as the Red Planet due to
    iron oxide on its surface.<br>

    Distance from Sun: <b>~228 million km</b><br>

    Orbital
    speed: <b>24 km/s</b><br>

    One year: <b>687 Earth days</b><br>

    It has
    the largest volcano (Olympus Mons) and signs of past water.<br><br>'
  planetName: Mars
