  planetInfo: '<b><u>Jupiter</u></b><br>

    Jupiter is the largest planet in the
    solar system and a gas giant.<br>

    Distance from Sun: <b>~778 million km</b><br>

    Orbital
    speed: <b>13 km/s</b><br>

    One year: <b>12 Earth years</b><br>

    It has
    a massive storm called the Great Red Spot and many moons.<br><br>'
  planetName: Jupiter
